  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>“<a href=\"/index.php/Oberyn_Martell\" title=\"Oberyn Martell\">Oberyn</a> was ever the viper. Deadly, dangerous, unpredictable. No man dared tread on him.” —<a href=\"/index.php/Doran_Martell\" title=\"Doran Martell\">Doran Martell</a> to the <a href=\"/index.php/Sand_Snakes\" title=\"Sand Snakes\">Sand Snakes</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd38.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd38.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p><div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd38.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd38.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_38\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 38\">Chapter 38</a>, The Watcher.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260406183707\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.007 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.007 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 110/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8414/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 327/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 22/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 527/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    4.186      1 -total\n100.00%    4.186      1 Template:Ref\n 63.29%    2.649      1 Template:Ref/core\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:26371-0!canonical and timestamp 20260406183707 and revision id 240819\n -->\n",
